TITLE: Querying Transaction by Hash in Reth
DESCRIPTION: Mermaid diagram illustrating the process of querying a transaction by its hash in Reth, showing the interaction between DatabaseProvider and StaticFileProvider based on transaction number.
SOURCE: https://github.com/paradigmxyz/reth/blob/main/crates/static-file/static-file/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_3

