TITLE: Checking for Math Library Dependency
DESCRIPTION: Determines if the math library (libm) is needed and sets the LIB_MATH variable accordingly.
SOURCE: https://github.com/paradigmxyz/reth/blob/main/crates/storage/libmdbx-rs/mdbx-sys/libmdbx/CMakeLists.txt#2025-04-16_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: cmake
CODE:
```
CHECK_FUNCTION_EXISTS(pow NOT_NEED_LIBM)
if(NOT_NEED_LIBM)
  set(LIB_MATH "")
else()
  set(CMAKE_REQUIRED_LIBRARIES m)
  CHECK_FUNCTION_EXISTS(pow HAVE_LIBM)
  if(HAVE_LIBM)
    set(LIB_MATH m)
  else()
    message(FATAL_ERROR "No libm found for math support")
  endif()
endif()
```

